description: The MSCI USA Minimum Volatility Index (USD) aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-cap US companies with low volatility scores Weighted dependant on volatility characteristics Reviewed on a semi annual basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI USA Minimum Volatility UCITS ETF 1D
